title: Replace SymbolicVariable uses with graph insert
body_html: SymbolicVariable have bunch of missing pieces to do the proper check (like shape info and schema), we need to update them to use graph.insert (which checks schema and handles default values), rather than graph.create, since now now graph.insert checks schema and inserts default values.
